This is mainly for AI. I guess this could be related to tick tank AI. In my case, slave miner needs this.

First the slave miner searches for ore then searches for a nearest deployable place.

The problem with GrantConditionOnDeploy::IsValidTerrain is that it can only check self.Location and doesn't allow planning checks from other traits or activities (not to mention it is private)

I'm proposing to modify the function as follows:

```
		public bool CanDeployAtLocation(CPos location)
		{
			return IsValidTerrainType(location) && IsValidRampType(location);
		}
```
